Suite Initialization
    ${GITHUB_REPO}=    RW.Core.Import User Variable    GITHUB_REPO
    ...    type=string
    ...    description=The GitHub Reposiroty to query
    ...    pattern=\w*
    ...    default=''
    ...    example=runwhen-contrib/helm-charts
